{"tid":380871,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實啲餐廳係咪奉旨唔收一千蚊","createTime":"2017-08-30T12:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T13:06:31.000Z","uid":25021,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"683f9d095ebf984445e1ea102bb188a17db856a6","tid":380871,"uid":25021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:49:41.000Z","msg":"上次去茶記食飯，唔記得斨錢全身得返一張一千蚊紙，去到收銀埋單已經say sorly話冇散紙，個肥婆收銀都要「㗩」尻我話我麻煩，叫我下次唔好，攪到我好似做錯事咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實啲餐廳有冇權去話唔收你一千蚊紙？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">死肥婆收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"56244ac850bc2dfb62064640da8b7d37939d433c","tid":380871,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:51:50.000Z","msg":"自從 2003 年一千蚊偽鈔嗰單野之後,  基本上 一千蚊 就收左皮"},{"pid":"906076213967988c1fd405b919e8142656361d65","tid":380871,"uid":61115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:55:28.000Z","msg":"你埋張單幾錢先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153ca31c94547eb7f7f857e4080f6bf9b5ed2ceb","tid":380871,"uid":25021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:59:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自從 2003 年一千蚊偽鈔嗰單野之後,  基本上 一千蚊 就收左皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我記得偽鈔之前冇鋪頭會標明唔收一千蚊(如果我記錯請屌)，過咗咁耐其實仲有偽鈔流通緊咩？<br />\n我感覺係鋪頭唔想準備咁多散紙斨俾人先食03年條水食到宜家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我理解佢哋，都唔係特登俾一千蚊埋單，點解要攪到好似我錯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7ef2f8d71ab6776da1113c7ac5333a74cefb40","tid":380871,"uid":25021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:03:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你埋張單幾錢先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三個人去食餐晏百幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係唔係有心俾大紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家1000蚊紙好似廢紙咁，收親都要諗辦法打散佢先有得用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8936373e214a461926c24ef8fc91994fdb1b33f3","tid":380871,"uid":59835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:03:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自從 2003 年一千蚊偽鈔嗰單野之後,  基本上 一千蚊 就收左皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我記得偽鈔之前冇鋪頭會標明唔收一千蚊(如果我記錯請屌)，過咗咁耐其實仲有偽鈔流通緊咩？<br />\n我感覺係鋪頭唔想準備咁多散紙斨俾人先食03年條水食到宜家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我理解佢哋，都唔係特登俾一千蚊埋單，點解要攪到好似我錯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實佢機底好多散紙<br />\n條肥婆純粹摺你腎虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaac3bffc9c394945319d5b568994a6364f1b051","tid":380871,"uid":25021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:06:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自從 2003 年一千蚊偽鈔嗰單野之後,  基本上 一千蚊 就收左皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我記得偽鈔之前冇鋪頭會標明唔收一千蚊(如果我記錯請屌)，過咗咁耐其實仲有偽鈔流通緊咩？<br />\n我感覺係鋪頭唔想準備咁多散紙斨俾人先食03年條水食到宜家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我理解佢哋，都唔係特登俾一千蚊埋單，點解要攪到好似我錯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實佢機底好多散紙<br />\n條肥婆純粹摺你腎虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係咪都俾肥婆㗩開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d0f5d6ba1bffc278d9ea9835b545773809b32cd","tid":380871,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:06:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自從 2003 年一千蚊偽鈔嗰單野之後,  基本上 一千蚊 就收左皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我記得偽鈔之前冇鋪頭會標明唔收一千蚊(如果我記錯請屌)，過咗咁耐其實仲有偽鈔流通緊咩？<br />\n我感覺係鋪頭唔想準備咁多散紙斨俾人先食03年條水食到宜家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我理解佢哋，都唔係特登俾一千蚊埋單，點解要攪到好似我錯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為 一千蚊面值大啲,  有偽鈔機會高啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}